milestones.description: Otieno and Hitesh Modi's 82-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 67 between Hitesh Modi and Ravi Shah
This is the lowest match aggregate (393) involving teams India & Kenya in ODIs
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (20) for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi
Tendulkar has scored 56 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Azharuddin's record
